# Cloudflare Pages `_headers` — cross-origin isolation for the threaded WebGPU build.
# Deploy the web-webgpu export directory to Cloudflare Pages with this file at its root.
# (Cloudflare Pages honors _headers; GitHub Pages and itch.io do not, which is why
# they can't boot the threaded build.)
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cache-Control: no-store
